## 3️⃣ 전이 규칙 설계 (Transition Rules)

### 3.1 유효한 전이만 허용

```rust
enum State { Idle, Running, Paused, Error }

fn can_transition(from: State, to: State) -> bool {
    match (from, to) {
        // 유효한 전이
        (State::Idle, State::Running) => true,
        (State::Running, State::Paused) => true,
        (State::Paused, State::Running) => true,
        (State::Running, State::Error) => true,
        (State::Error, State::Idle) => true,

        // 모든 다른 전이는 불가능
        _ => false,
    }
}
```

### 3.2 상태 전이 다이어그램

```
Idle ──START──> Running
 ▲               │  │
 │             │PAUSE│
 └STOP┘        │  │
              Paused
              │ │
              └STOP┘
                │
            (에러 발생)
                │
              Error
                │
             RECOVER
                │
                ▼
              Idle
```

### 3.3 전이 구현

```rust
fn transition(current: SystemState, command: &str) -> SystemState {
    match current {
        SystemState::Idle => {
            if command == "START" {
                SystemState::Running(10)
            } else {
                SystemState::Idle
            }
        }
        SystemState::Running(power) => {
            match command {
                "STOP" => SystemState::Idle,
                "POWER_UP" => SystemState::Running(power + 10),
                "ERROR" => SystemState::Error("문제 발생".to_string()),
                _ => SystemState::Running(power),
            }
        }
        SystemState::Error(_) => {
            if command == "RECOVER" {
                SystemState::Idle
            } else {
                current
            }
        }
    }
}
```

